Assault modification of the HK 416 rifle with an integrated grenade launcher.
Advantages:
 • High modularity and versatility - the ability to adjust weapons to any kind of combat;
 • High accuracy of fire, which allows to use weapons for sniping fire;
 • Due to the preservation of T-handle, weapon fits well in the hands, and the damper ihherited from the M16 allows a soft and smooth recoil;
 • Immune to corrosion.
Disadvantages:
 • The barrel of the weapon can be withdrawn from the aiming line while firing at full automatic.

